## Timeblocks

### v1

```plain text
7:30          | Wake Up
7:30 - 7:45   | Brush Teeth
7:45 - 8:15   | Create Timeblock
8:15 - 12:00  | Do practice exams for chemistry
12:00 - 15:00 | Chem exam
15:00 - 17:00 | Fixing/polishing the blog (loading screen), this should be my final technical change to the blog for some time
17:00 - 20:00 | Finish and implement AdminControl on my computers (i.e. get parents to enter secret code), goal is to finish my projects so that I won't need to work/maintain them when I start focusing on Precommit
20:00 - 21:00 | Finish Vue Lion
21:00 - 22:00 | Start creating a rough plan/timeline for Precommit for the coming months
22:00 - 23:15 | Evening Routine
```

## Routines

### Morning Routine

```plain text
7:00        | Wake Up
7:00 - 7:15 | Brush Teeth, Make Bed, Place Kindle on Pillow
7:15 - 7:30 | Breakfast
```

### Evening Routine

```plain text
22:00 - 22:25 | Check email; Create timeblock for next day
22:25 - 22:30 | Clear desk; Plug in devices
22:30 - 22:45 | Brush teeth; Quick shower
22:45 - 23:15 | Reading
23:15         | Bedtime; experiment with playing Weightless
```
